    <briefdescription>
<para>Drive a GPIO pin from a single bit of a DCS-BIOS output value. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Mirrors DcsBios::LED. Pin goes HIGH when (value &amp; mask) is non-zero, LOW otherwise.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Direct<sp/>STM32<sp/>GPIO:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1LED" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk::LED</ref><sp/>warn(A_4E_C_MASTER_CAUTION,<sp/>0x4000,<sp/>PB0);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
